4cf86489568","tid":2301250,"uid":78016,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"97babf3ab64d200ade32f926df50d3196e101941","tid":2301250,"uid":96708,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T08:24:00.000Z","msg":"病毒存在嘅意義就係想喺呢個世界永續落去<br />\n越多無病徵嘅人，呢隻病毒就越成功"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T13:04:52.000Z","msg":"如果香港多d 人識好似ching 咁諗可能已經無左限乜限乜令<br />\n越耐隻病毒只會越弱<br />\n假設起初係勁 到左宜家都係垃圾"},{"pid":"8299743db1e02da93b79ab038d5aac0074bd1368","tid":2301250,"uid":286206,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff91c4e5ac63af755c10a2ff6aca54cf86489568","tid":2301250,"uid":78016,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"97babf3ab64d200ade32f926df50d3196e101941","tid":2301250,"uid":96708,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T08:24:00.000Z","msg":"病毒存在嘅意義就係想喺呢個世界永續落去<br />\n越多無病徵嘅人，呢隻病毒就越成功"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T13:04:52.000Z","msg":"如果香港多d 人識好似ching 咁諗可能已經無左限乜限乜令<br />\n越耐隻病毒只會越弱<br />\n假設起初係勁 到左宜家都係垃圾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T13:22:29.000Z","msg":"病毒殺唔死你 但經濟崩潰必定可以殺死你<br />\n已經唔係講緊人生意義翻工呢D On9 野<br />\n底層隨時果班連開飯都係問題<br />\n再搞落去真係幾個% 有錢人玩哂 玩哂既意思係你生存空間都隨時無<br />\n而家香港跟本係集中營 唔覺架咩<br />\n仲有呢個痴線既世界 一有人中招就恥笑人<br />\n班人最好唔好出街唔好去超級市場唔好同朋友食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正常生活正常社交變左現代獵巫<br />\n就係為左香港一年只係死左十個人既病毒 <br />\n而且街上面人個mask好多應該都唔合規格(信藥房d貨？)"},{"pid":"53c354dbd33395bfdf0baa7fe2646adc58950b39","tid":2301250,"uid":68215,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T13:25:45.000Z","msg":"隻病毒識玩<br />\n全世界中晒又無病徵<br />\n就會退返晒啲技能點投資落致命性度<br />\n利申病毒公司"},{"pid":"329ff86f9beeec1ec456e4079f255a5f2a607537","tid":2301250,"uid":286206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T13:40:16.000Z","msg":"香港班所謂病毒學家日尻日講幾何級上昇又吹到十幾萬人中招<br />\n由年頭講到年尾 你個prediction由頭到尾都唔準<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多少少人中招就話你地唔夠努力防疫<br />\n最好笑一講班專家on9 就話你藍絲/廢老/熱狗<br />\n你真係覺得個口罩咁有用 有無試過係咪真係合規同埋好多人帶個口罩都係一日一個 除左落黎就揾個口罩袋入住佢 個口罩仲有用？(跟據醫生果D講法)  所謂專家跟本係想消滅人類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a487fd33f66346dc5b3c056a71110f042234b737","tid":2301250,"uid":152598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T13:55:47.000Z","msg":"啲測試其實準唔準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f37fbd22f7e9f2d6b2539093d37106a47641ad0d","tid":2301250,"uid":251026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T18:03:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/uPYFjDSG0JU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FuPYFjDSG0JU&d=ME9RTGLMBg%2Fi%2BHfTLk0cjIHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=cdce33a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uPYFjDSG0JU</a><br />\n想知咩事, 睇下發明PCR test嘅Mullis 點講 HIV=AIDS <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日嘅Covid1984係重演緊HIV=AIDS, 一樣係用PCR test大量製造false positive <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bc8b6aeacd45961aee52faf513613a2084f9239","tid":2301250,"uid":370010,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T18:13:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f5f3bd0b9970774f1a0903ce6ffce6a335649093","tid":2301250,"uid":251026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T04:59:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}